A startscript plugin for xsbt

To build this code, get and install SBT from 
    https://github.com/harrah/xsbt

Build and publish the plugin:
    git clone git@github.com:ritschwumm/xstb-scriptstart.git
    cd xstb-scriptstart
    sbt publish-local
    
Add the plugin to your project in project/plugins/build.sbt:
    addSbtPlugin("de.djini" % "xsbt-scriptstart" % "0.0.3")
    
Include the plugin in you project's build.sbt:

    seq(ScriptStartPlugin.allSettings:_*)

    scriptstartMainClass    := "my.Main"
    
    scriptstartVmArguments  := Seq("-Xmx192m")

Run the scriptstart task to get a directory containing all dependencies of 
your project together with startscripts for linux, os x, windows and os/2.
